---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Educational Scholarships | Veteran Support Services"
  description="Discover educational scholarships available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme. Learn about funding opportunities for further education and professional development.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Educational Scholarships for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) recognises the importance of education in supporting veterans' transition to civilian life. This page outlines the various educational scholarships and funding opportunities available to help you further your education and professional development.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Types of Scholarships</h2>
        <p>Several types of scholarships are available:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>University degree scholarships</li>
          <li>Vocational training grants</li>
          <li>Professional certification funding</li>
          <li>Research fellowships for postgraduate studies</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Eligibility Criteria</h2>
        <p>General eligibility requirements include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Proof of service in the UK Armed Forces</li>
          <li>Discharge papers or veteran status confirmation</li>
          <li>Meeting specific academic or professional prerequisites</li>
          <li>Demonstrating financial need (for some scholarships)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Application Process</h2>
        <p>Steps to apply for educational scholarships:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Research available scholarships and their requirements</li>
          <li>Gather necessary documentation (service records, academic transcripts, etc.)</li>
          <li>Complete the scholarship application form</li>
          <li>Write a personal statement or essay (if required)</li>
          <li>Submit your application before the deadline</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Partner Institutions</h2>
        <p>We have partnerships with various educational institutions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Universities offering dedicated veteran programmes</li>
          <li>Technical colleges with veteran-friendly policies</li>
          <li>Online learning platforms providing discounted courses</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Additional Support Services</h2>
        <p>Along with scholarships, we offer:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Educational counselling and career guidance</li>
          <li>Assistance with university and college applications</li>
          <li>Study skills workshops and academic support</li>
          <li>Mentoring programmes connecting veterans with academic advisors</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Related Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/support/career-transition" class="text-decoration-none">Career Transition Support</a></li>
              <li><a href="/financial/budgeting" class="text-decoration-none">Financial Planning</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/mental-health" class="text-decoration-none">Mental Health Support</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Scholarship Finder Tool</h3>
            <p>Use our scholarship finder tool to discover educational funding opportunities tailored to your needs and qualifications.</p>
            <a href="/scholarship-finder" class="btn btn-primary">Find Scholarships</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
